item.title: How do i set up my files for upload once i edit everything?
item.dc:creator: @doom_j doom_j
item.description:
@doom_j wrote:

Did you check to make sure you were port forwarded correctly?

You can use canyouseeme.org to check if your port is open. if you’re using no-ip make sure you have the correctly address in your client on your laptop or you won’t be able to connect.
